name: Rosalina (Mario)
description:
Trained on the animefull-final model for 9 epochs at a network dim of 128, then resized to a network dim of 64. Contains most of her official alternate outfits, though I had to remove a couple that were causing issues.

As usual, since this was trained on the animeful-pruned model, it will work well with any derivative merge.

The following tags are used:

Character: rosalina, luma, crown

Default outfit: blue dress

Fire Flower: red dress

Halloween: witch dress, witch hat

Biker: bikesuit

Swimwear: swimwear, flower

Chef: chef, apron

Tennis: tenniswear, white pantyhose

Volendam: volendamse dress, white hat

You can freely change her dress color by just putting the color you want before 'dress'. I tried to primarily keep her main attire faithful to the original, which means some of her alternate costumes which had a much smaller dataset to work with aren't 100% accurate.
